Interface DynamicTableModel

  • All Superinterfaces:
    TableModel
    All Known Implementing Classes:

    public interface DynamicTableModel
extends TableModel
    An interface that defines methods for adding and deleting rows from a tablemodel.

        boolean isRowEditable()
